            <div type="transcript" id="SH14-65">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>'Twas comfort in her dying room</l>
                    <l>To hear the living clock,</l>
                    <l>A short relief to have the wind</l>
                    <l>Walk boldly up and knock,</l>
                    <l>Diversion from the dying theme</l>
                    <l>To hear the children play,</l>
                    <l>But wrong, the mere</l>
                    <l>That these could live, --</l>
                    <l>And This of ours must die!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
